txt.en: The Yule Festival is upon us! Bundle up and brave the snow, for there is much to be accomplished.
Enjoy the Yule festivities while they last
The Yule Festival has made Middle-earth more lively during the long winter months.
A serene winter has settled upon Middle-earth in the parts yet untouched by the growing malice in the East, but some party-planners wish to enliven the cold winter days with some warm festivities.
